Label: Participant
Definition: Someone who takes part in an activity. [def-source: NCI]

Label: Head
Definition: The head is the anterior-most division of the body. [def-source: UBERON]

Label: Upper Leg
Definition: The part of the hindlimb between pelvis and the knee, corresponding to the femur. [def-source: UBERON]

Label: Upper Arm
Definition: The part of the forelimb between pectoral region and the elbow, corresponding to the humerus. [def-source: UBERON]

Label: Arm
Definition: The part of the forelimb extending from the shoulder to the autopod. [def-source: UBERON]

Label: Waist
Definition: The abdominal circumference at the navel. [def-source: NCI]
